commits.author: Uwe Schindler
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Like {@link #commit()}, but takes an additional commit data to be included * w/ the commit. *

* NOTE: some implementations may not support any custom data to be * included w/ the commit and may discard it altogether. Consult the actual * implementation documentation for verifying if this is supported. * * @see #prepareCommit() */ public void prepareCommit(Map commitData) throws IOException;
